OL,3,CPost Office IT investigators who
OL,4,Chelped uncover scandal to give evidence
OL,6,FTwo independent investigators who
OL,7,Fplayed a pivotal role in uncovering
OL,8,Fthe Horizon IT scandal are due to give
OL,9,Fevidence at the Post Office inquiry on
OL,10,FTuesday.
OL,12,FIn 2012, Ron Warmington and Ian
OL,13,FHenderson from Second Sight were
OL,14,Fbrought in to investigate potential
OL,15,Fissues with Horizon - the faulty IT
OL,16,Fsystem that made it look like money
OL,17,Fwas disappearing from Post Office
OL,18,Fbranches.
