OL,3,CPost Office IT investigators who
OL,4,Chelped uncover scandal to give evidence
OL,6,FThe accountants were hired by the Post
OL,7,FOffice after campaigners including
OL,8,Fformer sub-postmaster Alan Bates and
OL,9,Fthen MP James Arbuthnot had called for
OL,10,Fan independent investigation.
OL,12,FSecond Sight studied over 140 sub-
OL,13,Fpostmasters' claims and produced a
OL,14,Freport in 2013 finding that the
OL,15,FHorizon system was largely "flawed"
OL,16,Fand that Fujitsu, the creator, and
OL,17,Fmaintainer of Horizon, was altering
OL,18,Fbranch accounts.
