OL,3,CPost Office IT investigators who
OL,4,Chelped uncover scandal to give evidence
OL,6,FHowever, Second Sight said the Post
OL,7,FOffice "repeatedly refused" to
OL,8,Fconsider faults with the Horizon
OL,9,Fsystem.
OL,11,FSecret recordings obtained by ITV News
OL,12,Fearlier this year revealed proof of Mr
OL,13,FWarmington and Mr Henderson telling
OL,14,Fsenior Post Office bosses about their
OL,15,Fconcerns over the Horizon system.
OL,17,FOne recording was of a meeting held
OL,18,Fbetween the Post Office's top lawyer
OL,19,FChris Aujard and the two accountants
OL,20,Fin December 2013.
