OL,3,CPost Office IT investigators who
OL,4,Chelped uncover scandal to give evidence
OL,6,FIt shows the two men presented a
OL,7,Fdamning assessment of the Post
OL,8,FOffice's conduct in its investigations
OL,9,Fand prosecutions of sub-postmasters.
OL,11,FIn the recording, Mr Warmington tells
OL,12,FMr Aujard that the organisation is
OL,13,F"more defensive than any company I've
OL,14,Fever come across in my life",
OL,15,Fdescribing it as being "in total
OL,16,Fdenial that there was anything wrong
OL,17,Fat any point".
