OL,6,FLess than four months later, Post
OL,7,FOffice executives secretly decided to
OL,8,Fremove Second Sight from independently
OL,9,Finvestigating sub-postmasters' cases
OL,10,Fand bring the role in-house.
OL,12,FThe second recording was from a
OL,13,Fmeeting on January 5, 2015, between Mr
OL,14,FWarmington, and then Head of
OL,15,FPartnerships at the Post Office Angela
OL,16,FVan Den Bogerd.
