OL,3,CPost Office IT investigators who
OL,4,Chelped uncover scandal to give evidence
OL,6,FIn the phone call, Mr Warmington
OL,7,Fdiscusses the conviction of Carl Page
OL,8,Fwith Mrs Van Den Bogerd, and says the
OL,9,Fconviction was based on Horizon data
OL,10,Fon foreign exchange currency that he
OL,11,Fsays was inaccurate.
OL,13,FMrs Van Den Bogerd is heard in the
OL,14,Frecording agreeing that "we need to
OL,15,Ftake another look at this," confirming
OL,16,FMr Warmington had provided "further
OL,17,Finformation that is material to this
OL,18,Fcase."
