OL,4,Chelped uncover scandal to give evidence
OL,6,FHowever, Mr Page heard nothing from
OL,7,FMrs Van Den Bogerd or anyone at the
OL,8,FPost Office after this meeting.
OL,10,FHis conviction was not overturned for
OL,11,Fanother six years, during which time,
OL,12,Fhe attempted to take his own life.
OL,14,FThe Post Office has come under fire
OL,15,Ffollowing the screening of ITV drama
OL,16,FMr Bates Vs The Post Office, which put
OL,17,Fthe scandal under the spotlight.
